					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5831110#post-3789344</guid>
				<title>aaaaaaaaaaaaaaaahhhhhhh</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5831110/joey-fucknuts-takes-to-the-skies#post-3789344</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Thu, 03 May 2018 17:55:26 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Weryllium</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2727655</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I really can't express how much I love this tale.</p> <p>Not just because it features my creations (of course that's a factor), but I'm in awe in how you managed to breathe life into them. They sound <em>exactly</em> how I pictured them, and I have no idea how you did that. <strong>This</strong>, is the soul of the wiki IMO. Taking two completely disparate elements, and skillfully weaving them together in a way that makes sense and is pleasant to read.</p> <p>Joey remains an excellent and lovable character. His unique perspective lightens the mood, with his special brand of wisdom making us smile. He manages to be relatable despite being so strange; I think we've all felt like Joey at one time or another.</p> <p>+100, can't wait for the next one.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
