						 <p>I have since, re-doodled my boi Joey. Sans beard for funs sake.</p> <p>I really enjoyed all articles involving this lovable zomboy. Good job, my dude.</p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Joey&nbsp;Steelwings&nbsp;says&nbsp;goodbye</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Godspeed,&nbsp;ya&nbsp;nut&nbsp;fucker</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"><img src="https://i.imgur.com/4SAubd0.jpg" alt="4SAubd0.jpg" class="image" /></div> </div> </div> 
